content: On the television show The Walking Dead, which original characters from the first season were still alive and present at the end of the series, after 11 seasons?

chosen: At the end of the final episode of The Walking Dead, Rick Grimes (Andrew Lincoln), Daryl Dixon (Norman Reedus) and Carol Peletier (Melissa McBride) are the only surviving original characters.
rejected: At the end of the final season of The Walking Dead, only two of the original characters from Season 1 remained: Rick Grimes and Michonne. However, both had been absent for several seasons prior to the finale.
